</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11961505-david">David</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It depends. John had a unique perspective on the human condition. He understood broken people, and broken souls, more than any modern American writer.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It depends. John had a unique perspective on the human condition. He understood broken people, and broken souls, more than any modern American writer. The book has some amazingly well written parts that exemplify his understanding of damaged people. I totally recommend finding a copy of this book, and Stripper Lessons, his other completed work.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
